      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ARCANE (7) was speedy out of box 1 on debut to score by 4.5 lengths (25.78) at this track over 450m. Drawn wide but has good early pace. Expected to go close again. DOOGIE MCGRAW (8) ran a nice race two back to fill a minor placing then got off the mark last time (25.44) at this track over 450m. Boxed wide here. Can measure up again. GUS THE GANGSTER (1) was safely held on debut after settling well back when fourth (26.42) at this track over 450m. Has the inside draw this time. Expecting sharp improvement this line-up. LIVING LEGEND (2) finished in the placings last start and deserves some thought.",
